from me, okay?

51:03.920 --> 51:06.685
Now, I could lose my job
just talkin' to you right now.

51:06.720 --> 51:09.451
- OLSON: Go on, Deputy.
- MIKE: Well, they brought in

51:09.480 --> 51:12.211
some forensics hot shot
from the city.

51:12.240 --> 51:13.844
Now you're suspect.

51:13.880 --> 51:15.564
OLSON:
Oh, you think I'm a suspect?

51:15.600 --> 51:18.649
They shot my goddamn ear off.

51:18.720 --> 51:20.449
I'm disabled. MIKE: I know it.

51:20.480 --> 51:23.609
OLSON: I could take my goddamn
pension and walk away.

51:23.640 --> 51:26.450
But I want to find the son
of a bitch who killed Sam.

51:26.520 --> 51:28.010
Figure that.

51:28.040 --> 51:30.168
MIKE: I know. We all know.

51:30.200 --> 51:31.725
