51:33.480 --> 51:34.891
There's just something
that don't add up

51:34.920 --> 51:36.251
about that crime scene.

51:36.320 --> 51:38.687
OLSON: You want to know
what don't add up?

51:38.720 --> 51:40.290
They lost the body.

51:40.320 --> 51:42.766
