to Sam's death without a body?

51:42.800 --> 51:45.201
Tell me that.
MIKE: Well, they lost the body,

51:45.240 --> 51:47.163
but not before
some brown nosin' intern

51:47.200 --> 51:50.044
pulled the slug from the kid
before he was missin'.

51:50.080 --> 51:52.526
Ballistics had a match...

51:52.560 --> 51:55.769
for your gun.

51:55.840 --> 51:59.606
OLSON: I'm being set up, Deputy,
and you know it.

51:59.640 --> 52:02.120
MIKE:
I do, but... rules are rules.

52:02.160 --> 52:03.969
I'm sorry, Sheriff.
I got to take you in.

52:04.000 --> 52:05.968
Now, these things
kind of sort themselves out,

52:06.000 --> 52:08.048
so you got to trust me here.

52:08.080 --> 52:10.481
OLSON: Now, Mike...

52:10.520 --> 52:12.807
you know
that's not gonna happen.

52:12.840 --> 52:15.491
I'd be dead before breakfast.

52:15.520 --> 52:18.091
MIKE: I don't think
the DEA's gonna go that far.

52:18.120 --> 52:21.408
OLSON:
You know who Sam's old man is?

52:21.440 --> 52:23.841
Mateo Perez.

52:23.880 --> 52:25.882
MIKE: The Mateo Perez?

52:25.920 --> 52:27.968
