and hand him over.

52:33.760 --> 52:35.489
MIKE:
Well, what are you gonna do?

52:35.520 --> 52:37.727
OLSON: I'm gonna find this son
of a bitch and hand him over.

52:37.760 --> 52:39.330
MIKE: Well, what if you don't?

52:39.360 --> 52:41.203
OLSON: You and I have seen
enough dead bodies of people

52:41.240 --> 52:42.571
who have tangled with him

52:42.600 --> 52:45.683
to know that you don't tangle
with Mateo Perez.

52:45.720 --> 52:49.441
Now, you know goddamn well
I didn't kill Sam.

52:49.480 --> 52:53.007
I just need a little time
to get out from underneath this.

52:53.040 --> 52:54.326
MIKE: All right.

52:54.360 --> 52:56.601
I'll tell you what I'm gonna do.

52:56.640 --> 52:58.244
I'm gonna forget the DEA.

52:58.320 --> 52:59.765
What the hell they doin',
comin' in here

52:59.800 --> 53:02.644
and tellin' us
our business anyway. Right?

53:02.680 --> 53:04.569
You go take care
of that business.

53:04.600 --> 53:08.286
I was never here,
and neither were you.

53:08.320 --> 53:10.971
OLSON: Thanks, Mike.

53:11.040 --> 53:12.246
MIKE: You turn yourself in

53:12.280 --> 53:14.203
