53:19.560 --> 53:21.881
OLSON:
I want to know where the DEA

53:21.920 --> 53:24.730
is concentratin'
their investigation.

53:24.760 --> 53:27.001
Give me something... anything.

53:27.040 --> 53:30.044
They shut me out,
and time is running out.

53:30.080 --> 53:31.923
MIKE: I'll see
what I can come up with.

53:31.960 --> 53:33.769
OLSON: I owe you.

53:33.800 --> 53:36.201
