56:30.600 --> 56:32.045
Your husband
will come after you.

56:32.080 --> 56:33.684
CHRISTINE:
There are ways around that.

56:33.720 --> 56:35.245
We could just kill him.

56:35.280 --> 56:36.884
BRIAN: No.
We ain't doin' that now.

56:36.920 --> 56:38.968
CHRISTINE:
All right, well, just vanish

56:39.040 --> 56:41.122
