BRIAN: What the fuck is that?

56:48.920 --> 56:51.002
- CHRISTINE: Shit!
- BRIAN: God damn it!

56:51.040 --> 56:53.247
[Blaring continues]

56:57.880 --> 56:59.370
CHRISTINE: Shit.

56:59.400 --> 57:00.686
[ Blaring stops]

57:00.720 --> 57:02.245
The phone's dead.

57:03.040 --> 57:06.089
No calls out until the security
company calls and clears it.

57:06.120 --> 57:07.929
They'll send a car
if no one answers.

57:07.960 --> 57:10.440
BRIAN: We got to go now.
You understand? Come on.

57:12.600 --> 57:14.250
- HOWARD: Help!
- CHRISTINE: No. Leave him!

57:14.280 --> 57:16.362
HOWARD: Help.
There's a fire in here!

57:16.400 --> 57:18.687
Help! Help!

57:20.320 --> 57:22.607
Come into my fuckin' house!

57:27.520 --> 57:28.601
[Gun clatters]

57:31.800 --> 57:32.881
BRIAN: Fuck you, man!

57:32.920 --> 57:35.605
[ Spits ]

57:35.680 --> 57:38.047
HOWARD: Aah!

57:42.040 --> 57:45.249
My fuckin' nose.

57:47.560 --> 57:50.928
What are you doin'?

57:52.360 --> 57:54.806
