57:54.840 --> 57:57.411
CHRISTINE: Back off.

57:57.440 --> 57:59.886
HOWARD: Wha... What?

57:59.920 --> 58:01.445
BRIAN: Okay.

58:01.480 --> 58:03.164
CHRISTINE: Back the hell up.

58:04.840 --> 58:07.411
I will shoot you.

58:07.440 --> 58:09.488
BRIAN: Really?

58:09.520 --> 58:11.602
CHRISTINE: Plans change.

58:11.640 --> 58:14.120
Sex was good and all,
but you're a little boring.

58:14.160 --> 58:18.324
Plus, that's a lot of money.

58:18.360 --> 58:21.887
Give me the keys... now!

58:26.760 --> 58:28.762
HOWARD: What are you doin'?

58:31.960 --> 58:35.009
How long you been fuckin' him?
Huh?

58:39.080 --> 58:42.687
You pathetic bitch.

58:42.720 --> 58:44.324
I fuckin' hate you.

58:44.360 --> 58:45.850
You know what?

58:45.880 --> 58:48.850
You're gonna end up right back
in that trailer-trash park

58:48.920 --> 58:50.251
that I found you in.

58:50.280 --> 58:53.090
CHRISTINE: I will shoot you.

58:55.080 --> 58:58.527
BRIAN: It was
all about the money, huh, Chris?

58:58.560 --> 59:00.210
CHRISTINE: It's always
about the money, honey.

59:00.240 --> 59:02.925
Now get me the fucking money!

59:05.240 --> 59:06.890
