59:13.080 --> 59:16.766
Oh, baby.

59:16.800 --> 59:20.521
You know, maybe we should
just get married.

59:20.560 --> 59:22.801
That way I can get you
your green card.

59:25.280 --> 59:28.841
Things work out, maybe
I'll even get you a boob job.

59:28.880 --> 59:30.644
